-- FAW Group May Be Restructuring Business for IPO, Securities Times Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-13T23:34:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/faw-group-may-be-restructuring-business-for-ipo-securities-times-reports.html

          
          
             FAW Group Corp. may be restructuring
its business as part of preparations to list the group as a
whole, the Securities Times reported today, without citing
anyone.  
